{{Infobox scientist |name = Walter Minder |image = |image_size = |caption = |birth_date = {{birth date|1905|8|6}} |birth_place = [[Seeland (Switzerland)|Seeland]], [[Switzerland]] |nationality = [[Switzerland|Swiss]] |death_date = {{death date and age|1992|4|1|1905|8|6}} |death_place = [[Bern]], [[Switzerland]] |residence = |field = |work_institution =[[University of Bern]] |alma_mater = [[University of Bern]] |doctoral_advisor = [[Emil Hugi]] |doctoral_students = |known_for = |prizes = |religion = |footnotes = }}
'''Walter Minder''' (August 6, 1905 – April 1, 1992) was a [[Swiss]] [[mineralogist]] and [[chemist]].<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sgsmp.ch/honmem/minder.htm | title = Walter Minder (06.08.1905 - 01.04.1992)}}</ref> He together with [[Alice Leigh-Smith]] announced the discovery of element 85 (now called [[astatine]])<ref name="Ru1968">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1070/RC1968v037n02ABEH001603 | title = Astatine | year = 1968 | author = Nefedov, V D | journal = Russian Chemical Reviews | volume = 37 | issue = 2 | pages = 87 | last2 = Norseev | first2 = Yu V | last3 = Toropova | first3 = M A | last4 = Khalkin | first4 = Vladimir A | bibcode=1968RuCRv..37...87N}}</ref> in 1940<ref name="helv1940">{{cite journal | doi =10.1038/146225a0 | title =Element 85 | year =1940 | journal =Nature | volume =146 | issue =3694 | pages =225 | bibcode=1940Natur.146Q.225.}}</ref> and 1942.<ref name="anglo1942">{{cite journal | title = Experimental Evidence of the Existence of Element 85 in the Thorium Family | author = Alice Leigh-Smith, Walter Minder | journal = Nature | volume = 150 | issue = 3817 | pages = 767&ndash;768 | year = 1942 | doi = 10.1038/150767a0 | bibcode=1942Natur.150..767L}}</ref> He proposed the name [[helvetium]] in 1940<ref name="helv1940"/> and [[anglohelvetium]]<ref name="anglo1942"/> in 1942 for the new element. Later it was proven that in fact he had not discovered element 85.<ref name="Ru1968"/><ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1007/BF01487965 | title = Über eine vermutete ß-Strahlung des Radium A und die natürliche Existenz des Elementes 85 | year = 1942 | author = Karlik, Berta | journal = Naturwissenschaften | volume = 30 | issue = 44-45 | pages = 685 | last2 = Bernert | first2 = Traude | bibcode=1942NW.....30..685K}}</ref>
